  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SURVIVE, EXPLORE, REPEAT</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive against waves of enemies in quick, intense rounds as you explore the randomly generated dungeons. Your cursor becomes the hero, battling against foes in a bullet hell frenzy that tests your reflexes, precision, and decision-making.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339780/extras/fdef3c2e23e2ef25dbe8fabf418ac412.poster.avif?t=1747755040\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339780/extras/fdef3c2e23e2ef25dbe8fabf418ac412.webm?t=1747755040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339780/extras/fdef3c2e23e2ef25dbe8fabf418ac412.mp4?t=1747755040\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PLAY ON YOUR DESKTOP</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Desktop Survivors 98 doesn’t play in a window — it plays over your desktop. Enemies, upgrades, and chaos unfold across your real screen.<br><br>Whether you’re looking for a quick break or an extended challenge, <strong>Desktop Survivors 98</strong> fits perfectly into your routine. With its fast-paced rounds and the ability to toggle the game   at any moment, you’re always just a click away from diving back into the action.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339780/extras/b97589589c9d98f13bf924e8bf257b56.poster.avif?t=1747755040\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339780/extras/b97589589c9d98f13bf924e8bf257b56.webm?t=1747755040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339780/extras/b97589589c9d98f13bf924e8bf257b56.mp4?t=1747755040\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play Directly on Your Desktop</strong>: The action unfolds right on your desktop, overlaying seamlessly over anything you’re doing—perfect for multitasking!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cursor Combat</strong>: Your cursor becomes the hero, engaging in progressively fast-paced battles against waves of enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dangerous Enemy Waves</strong>: Survive relentless hordes in a bullet hell experience that challenges your skills and reaction time.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Variety of Weapons and Upgrades</strong>: Discover, acquire, and upgrade powerful  items as you progress.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Nostalgic Aesthetic</strong>: Immerse yourself in retro-inspired visuals that capture the charm of classic PC gaming.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Take a Break Anytime</strong>: Toggle the game on or off at any moment to pause, step away, and return whenever you’re ready.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SURVIVE, EXPLORE, REPEAT</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive against waves of enemies in quick, intense rounds as you explore the randomly generated dungeons. Your cursor becomes the hero, battling against foes in a bullet hell frenzy that tests your reflexes, precision, and decision-making.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339780/extras/fdef3c2e23e2ef25dbe8fabf418ac412.poster.avif?t=1747755040\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339780/extras/fdef3c2e23e2ef25dbe8fabf418ac412.webm?t=1747755040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339780/extras/fdef3c2e23e2ef25dbe8fabf418ac412.mp4?t=1747755040\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PLAY ON YOUR DESKTOP</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Desktop Survivors 98 doesn’t play in a window — it plays over your desktop. Enemies, upgrades, and chaos unfold across your real screen.<br><br>Whether you’re looking for a quick break or an extended challenge, <strong>Desktop Survivors 98</strong> fits perfectly into your routine. With its fast-paced rounds and the ability to toggle the game   at any moment, you’re always just a click away from diving back into the action.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339780/extras/b97589589c9d98f13bf924e8bf257b56.poster.avif?t=1747755040\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339780/extras/b97589589c9d98f13bf924e8bf257b56.webm?t=1747755040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339780/extras/b97589589c9d98f13bf924e8bf257b56.mp4?t=1747755040\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play Directly on Your Desktop</strong>: The action unfolds right on your desktop, overlaying seamlessly over anything you’re doing—perfect for multitasking!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cursor Combat</strong>: Your cursor becomes the hero, engaging in progressively fast-paced battles against waves of enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dangerous Enemy Waves</strong>: Survive relentless hordes in a bullet hell experience that challenges your skills and reaction time.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Variety of Weapons and Upgrades</strong>: Discover, acquire, and upgrade powerful  items as you progress.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Nostalgic Aesthetic</strong>: Immerse yourself in retro-inspired visuals that capture the charm of classic PC gaming.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Take a Break Anytime</strong>: Toggle the game on or off at any moment to pause, step away, and return whenever you’re ready.</p></li></ul>",
